{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":540234,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":112681,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"人们期望将情感支持、性满足、共同爱好、智性刺激和和谐的共同育儿等要求堆进同一辆购物车。但这似乎是一件愈来愈不可能完成的任务。","timestamp":1605061273,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":540244,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":112681,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"破防了","timestamp":1605061545,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":540257,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":112681,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 呜呜呜","timestamp":1605061900,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":540261,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":112681,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 求问出处，以便拜读","timestamp":1605061925,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":540334,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":112681,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 公众号“利维坦”，今天的新文~\n（p.s.包含较多 多元关系 的讨论，请酌情参考哈","timestamp":1605063213,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":112681,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"“当我们把所有的亲密需求都集中到一个人身上时，我们实际上会让这段关系变得更加脆弱。”在这种对恋爱关系的期望下，如果伴侣在哪怕一个方面做得不够好，我们也会无法得到精神上的缓冲。这种期望也扼杀了我们想象其他人如何扮演（我们生活中的）重要角色的能力，这些角色包括同居者、护理人或知己。","timestamp":1605061223,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782642,"url":"","vote":{}}}